{"tid":907735,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【樓奴】港島百億豪宅變530間劏房被釘契　政府下令發展商急還原","createTime":"2018-11-19T04:46:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T22:58:55.000Z","uid":121464,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8d12abbd1b046bfb50ff81820460b981ecf765e4","tid":907735,"uid":121464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T04:46:56.000Z","msg":"近年一提起「劏房」，均會想到擠迫的環境、翳焗的空氣和辛酸的臉孔。把物業改建成劏房出租，租金回報隨時倍增，亦令豪宅業主動心。菲律賓華人陳永裁家族為大股東的裕景興業，就分別把山頂、赤柱和深水灣三個用作收租的豪宅變成豪華劏房出租，其中兩個包裝成共居概念，由裕景興業旗下的公司管理，每間房只有60至120呎，另外山頂的獨立屋就劏成1,000多呎的單位。<br />\n不過《香港01》發現，上述三個屋苑，均在今年被地政總署「釘契」，署方稱業主正還原單位。裕景興業旗下營運公寓的公司回應，指正處理違契事宜。<br />\n<br />\n其他呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3efa85b8a8cd2322a24efd3c270ae72e026961","tid":907735,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:07:43.000Z","msg":"沒收就fat fat"},{"pid":"8f6cd6eaa76c953e85993066a0474bdcef939610","tid":907735,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"傾緊點修例比佢合法搞咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53fff6dfbff0832f9c52547be5c9b660ff2f7d25","tid":907735,"uid":156376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f6cd6eaa76c953e85993066a0474bdcef939610","tid":907735,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:09:58.000Z","msg":"傾緊點修例比佢合法搞咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:12:26.000Z","msg":"每間劏房不少於60尺不違法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffd9da07aede645ec2d5f1304953b051fc0052a","tid":907735,"uid":43225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T06:36:15.000Z","msg":"點解呢d地段都要做劏房"},{"pid":"ceae18d4c7bc82ddac97e4ec05e68e352337679e","tid":907735,"uid":18395,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"bffd9da07aede645ec2d5f1304953b051fc0052a","tid":907735,"uid":43225,"like"